{"tid":1860110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"支那公開乞討口罩、防護衣和護目鏡裝備","createTime":"2020-02-03T13:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T15:51:14.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b749174301c6871be0904f3043641cb88e9b7c22","tid":1860110,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"法新社報導，中國大陸外交部發言人華春瑩3日在記者會上說，大陸「急需」口罩和防護衣。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說：「中國目前急需醫療口罩、防護衣和護目鏡。」<br />\n <br />\n根據工信部的資料，大陸目前每天最多只能生產2000萬片口罩。工信部3日稍早表示，正加緊從歐洲、日本和美國進口口罩。"},{"pid":"31b7e69b62e4f83872799545dd5ba1088486024e","tid":1860110,"uid":53577,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"扮弱者啫<br />\n<br />\n支那乜都有, 口罩每日20億都冇問題(真)"},{"pid":"e0c20bcaa98bf37b79740e22ee87b728617478da","tid":1860110,"uid":183844,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"早2日先炸咗3箱N95<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"67e830029455a44d77c9646ff8630d233c731784","tid":1860110,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 支那賤畜一刻都不能幫"},{"pid":"4ea82a319f532e170a7953bf6152ca1b9ad301ef","tid":1860110,"uid":230759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"支那經濟就快走上世界第一，但係而家連咁基本既野都做唔到"},{"pid":"f74eb4d2524b856cbe12be0d2aac21be674b1e9a","tid":1860110,"uid":49643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"一時又話要, 一時又話不缺, 即係點"},{"pid":"b7dba9536c4aa8ab36365adc2f21d9b62adbecf2","tid":1860110,"uid":103783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力"},{"pid":"23ee88a67c48c1f597718a6d21be869e77b17113","tid":1860110,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"跪係到求美國爹先考慮"},{"pid":"8f52ab5781cdd934203c04859a821e9aafc6bf98","tid":1860110,"uid":229948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:44: